\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $\left(X,\zeta\right)$
\end_inset

的取值范围是
\begin_inset Formula $0<X<1$
\end_inset

，
\begin_inset Formula $0<\zeta<1$
\end_inset

。区间划分是
\begin_inset Formula $\left(0,\zeta,1\right),\left(0,1-\zeta,1\right)$
\end_inset

。由于分界点不同，所以需要考虑
\begin_inset Formula $\zeta$
\end_inset

与
\begin_inset Formula $1-\zeta$
\end_inset

的大小关系，一共四种情况，
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\left(1,1\right) &  & 0<y<\zeta,0<y<1-\zeta & \Rightarrow\left(0<\zeta<\frac{1}{2}\land0<y<\zeta\right)\lor\left(\frac{1}{2}<\zeta<1\land0<y<1-\zeta\right)\\
\left(1,2\right) &  & 0<y<\zeta,1-\zeta<y<1 & \Rightarrow\frac{1}{2}<\zeta<1\land1-\zeta<y<\zeta\\
\left(2,1\right) &  & \zeta<y<1,0<y<1-\zeta & \Rightarrow0<\zeta<\frac{1}{2}\land\zeta<y<1-\zeta\\
\left(2,2\right) &  & \zeta<y<1,1-\zeta<y<1 & \Rightarrow\left(0<\zeta\leq\frac{1}{2}\land1-\zeta<y<1\right)\lor\left(\frac{1}{2}<\zeta<1\land\zeta<y<1\right)
\end{align*}

\end_inset

也就是
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
